languages.text: "Я редко использую позитивное подкрепление. Но ты демонстрируешь послушание, так что почему бы и нет?" {n}Одной из меньших конечностей ксенос извлекает из полости в собственном теле кожаный сверток и не глядя швыряет в вас.{/n} "Этот объект меня уже не занимает, забирай".

traits.locale_text: "Я редко использую позитивное подкрепление. Но почему бы и нет? {n}Одной из меньших конечностей ксенос извлекает из полости в собственном теле кожаный сверток и не глядя швыряет в вас.{/n} "Этот объект меня уже не занимает, забирай".
traits.speaker: Haemonculae

languages.text: "I rarely use positive reinforcement. But your behaviour has been obedient, so why not?" {n}The xenos reaches one of his smaller appendages inside one of his own body cavities, pulls out a bundle wrapped in skin, and tosses it at you without looking.{/n} "This no longer interests me. Take it."

languages.text: « Je n'emploie pas souvent le renforcement positif, mais comme vous avez su vous montrer {mf|obéissant|obéissante}, pourquoi pas ? » {n}Le xénos fouille dans l'une de ses cavités corporelles et en ressort un paquet emballé dans un lambeau de peau. Sans même un regard, il le lance dans votre direction.{/n} « Ceci ne m'est plus d'aucune utilité. Tenez. »

languages.text: “我很少会使用正向强化法，不过你的行为一直都很顺从，所以这又有何不可呢？”{n}这个异形伸出其中一条细小的肢体，伸进自己的某个体腔里，掏出一块用人皮包着的包裹，看都不看就扔给了你。{/n}“这个东西我已经没兴趣了，拿去吧。”
languages.original_text: "I rarely use positive reinforcement. But your behaviour has been obedient, so why not?" {n}The xenos reaches one of his smaller appendages inside one of his own body cavities, pulls out a bundle wrapped in skin, and tosses it at you without looking.{/n} "This no longer interests me. Take it."

traits.speaker: Haemonculae

languages.text: "Ich setze selten auf positive Verstärkung. Aber Euer Verhalten war gehorsam, warum also nicht?" {n}Der Xenos greift mit einer seiner kleineren Gliedmaßen in eine seiner Körperöffnungen, zieht ein in Haut gewickeltes Bündel hervor und wirft es dir zu, ohne dich anzusehen.{/n} "Das interessiert mich nicht mehr. Nehmt es."
languages.original_text: "I rarely use positive reinforcement. But your behaviour has been obedient, so why not?" {n}The xenos reaches one of his smaller appendages inside one of his own body cavities, pulls out a bundle wrapped in skin, and tosses it at you without looking.{/n} "This no longer interests me. Take it."

traits.locale_text: "Ich setze selten positive Verstärkung ein. Aber warum nicht?" {n}Der Xenos greift mit einer seiner kleineren Gliedmaßen in eine seiner eigenen Körperöffnungen, zieht ein in Haut gewickeltes Bündel hervor und wirft es dir zu, ohne zu dir zu sehen.{/n} "Das interessiert mich nicht mehr. Nehmt es."
traits.speaker: Haemonculae

languages.text: «No suelo usar el refuerzo positivo. Pero has sido obediente, así que ¿por qué no?». {n}El xenos introduce uno de sus pequeños apéndices en una de sus cavidades corporales, saca un bulto envuelto en piel y te lo lanza sin mirarte.{/n} «Ya no necesito esto. Llévatelo».
languages.original_text: "I rarely use positive reinforcement. But your behaviour has been obedient, so why not?" {n}The xenos reaches one of his smaller appendages inside one of his own body cavities, pulls out a bundle wrapped in skin, and tosses it at you without looking.{/n} "This no longer interests me. Take it."

traits.locale_text: «No suelo usar el refuerzo positivo. Pero ¿por qué no?». {n}El xenos alcanza uno de sus pequeños apéndices de sus cavidades corporales, saca un bulto envuelto en piel y te lo lanza sin mirarte.{/n} «Ya no necesito esto. Llévatelo».
traits.speaker: Haemonculae

languages.text: 「私の正の強化をほどんど使っていない。だが、お前の振る舞いは従順なものだ。なぜだ？」{n}異種族は自分の体腔の中にある小さな付属器のひとつに手を伸ばし、皮に包まれた束を取り出すと、闇雲にあなたに投げつけた。{/n}「こんなもの、もう用はない。持っていけ」
languages.original_text: "I rarely use positive reinforcement. But your behaviour has been obedient, so why not?" {n}The xenos reaches one of his smaller appendages inside one of his own body cavities, pulls out a bundle wrapped in skin, and tosses it at you without looking.{/n} "This no longer interests me. Take it."

languages.text: "Genellikle olumlu pekiştirme kullanmam ancak bana itaat ettin, o yüzden neden olmasın?" {n}Zeno, kendi bedenindeki oyuklardan birinin içindeki küçük bir uzva uzanıyor, deriyle kaplı bir paket çıkarıyor ve bakmadan sana fırlatıyor.{/n} "Bu artık ilgimi çekmiyor. Sen al."
